\", \"from\": 174, \"to\": 182}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic Summer Games\", \"from\": 187, \"to\": 211}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Grammy-winner delivered a spirited rendition of Ren\\u00e9e \\\"Zizi\\\" Jeanmaire's \\\"Mon Truc en Plumes\\\" (\\\"My Feathery Thing\\\"), decked out in a black leotard and opera gloves surrounded by dancers donning round pink feathered adornments.\", \"from\": 215, \"to\": 445, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The Grammy-winner\", \"from\": 215, \"to\": 232}, {\"ngram\": \"a spirited rendition\", \"from\": 243, \"to\": 263}, {\"ngram\": \"Ren\\u00e9e \\\"Zizi\\\" Jeanmaire's \\\"Mon Truc\", \"from\": 267, \"to\": 301}, {\"ngram\": \"Plumes\", \"from\": 305, \"to\": 311}, {\"ngram\": \"My Feathery Thing\", \"from\": 315, \"to\": 332}, {\"ngram\": \"a black leotard and opera gloves\", \"from\": 350, \"to\": 382}, {\"ngram\": \"dancers\", \"from\": 397, \"to\": 404}, {\"ngram\": \"round pink feathered adornments\", \"from\": 413, \"to\": 444}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After proclaiming, \\\"Bonsoir et bienvenue \\u00e0 Paris,\\\" which translates to, \\\"Good evening and welcome to Paris,\\\" Gaga danced and traipsed down a staircase on the riverbank surrounded by her dancers with feathers.\", \"from\": 447, \"to\": 655, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 467, \"end\": 474, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bonsoir_(film)\", \"score\": 0.934115051658946, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Bonsoir\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\", \"Q11424\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bonsoir_(film)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Bonsoir_(film)\"}, {\"begin\": 490, \"end\": 495, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999022293, \"rank\": 9.775272189447297e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 548, \"end\": 553, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9